# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# PostHog analytics (PRO-22)
# Privacy-first, cookieless. No cookies required for basic page view tracking.
# Obtain your project API key from: https://eu.posthog.com/settings/project
# Leave NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY empty to disable analytics entirely.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=
# EU region (GDPR-friendly default). Switch to https://us.i.posthog.com if needed.
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://eu.i.posthog.com

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Gemini — Vivi chat (POST /api/chat)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Server-only. Obtain from Google AI Studio. Paste exactly into Vercel Production; revoked or mistyped keys
# still pass build but Gemini returns errors at runtime (empty stream unless fixed).
GEMINI_API_KEY=
#
# Enables the FAB and /api/chat. Set to lowercase true locally and in Vercel for production builds.
NEXT_PUBLIC_AI_ENABLED=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Vercel production checklist (vivi-chat)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. In Vercel → Project → Environment Variables → Production, set BOTH:
#    - NEXT_PUBLIC_AI_ENABLED=true  (literal; case-sensitive)
#    - GEMINI_API_KEY=<valid Google AI Studio / Gemini API key> (paste exactly; revoked keys yield empty streams)
# 2. After adding/changing NEXT_PUBLIC_* you MUST redeploy (new build inlines client env).
# 3. Optional: Preview env needs NEXT_PUBLIC_AI_ENABLED per branch unless you attach "all previews".
# 4. npm run build on Vercel Production runs scripts/verify-vercel-ai-production.mjs to fail
#    the build early if Production is missing AI flags/server key.
